        "type": "apiKey",
        "in": "header",
        "name": "X-Auth",
        "description": "HMAC-SHA256 authentication. The X-Auth header value is formatted as '{api_key}:{hmac_digest}'. The HMAC message is constructed by concatenating the API key, server time (X-Time header), nonce (X-Nonce header), empty string, organization ID (X-Organization-Id header), empty string, HTTP method, path, query string, and request body (if present), each separated by a null byte (\\x00). Additional required headers: X-Time (server timestamp), X-Nonce (unique UUID), X-Organization-Id (your org ID), X-Request-Id (unique request UUID)."
      }
    },
